extendedInfo.description: If you are Fall Out Boy's fan, this app is right for you. Whenever you want to check Fall Out Boy's lyrics, just open this app and choose the lyrics that you want. You don't have to access the internet to get the lyrics. We provide all Fall Out Boy's lyrics here. In the Album tab, you can choose lyrics based on the album. In All lyrics tab, all of Fall Out Boy's lyrics are here. You can quickly search the lyrics by using the search bar at the top of the page.Hope you guy enjoy using this app as much as I enjoy developing it. :)************************Main Features
